\id JON Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h JONAH
\toc1 JONAH
\toc2 Jonah
\toc3 Jon
\mt1 JONAH
\mt2 (The Book of Jonah)
\is1 Jonah Cabu Kawng
\im Jonah cabu he Bible dongah a tloe tonghma rhoek neh vai uh pawh. Jonah he a tloe tonghma olphong bangla om pawh. He tah Pathen kah a khuenah neh tonghma loh a oeinah kawng he kungpuei la a thui. A lungdueng la thui koinih Pathen kah lungnah tah hlangboeih ham he a rhal rhoek ham pataeng om. Assyria kho Nineveh he a tholh phu dantat ham a om coeng dongah cet lamtah thui pah a ti nah. Pathen ol a ngai kolla tuisangpho dongah \png Sapain (Tarshish)\png* la yong. Pathen loh hlipuei a tloh tloe la a tueih pa tih tuisangpho khaw dalh buek. Jonah loh Pathen ol a ngai pawt dongah ni hlipuei loh tui sangpho dalh a buek sak tila kholong pathen aka bawk rhoek loh a ming. Te dongah Jonah kah Pathen \nd Yahweh\nd* te a bawk uh tih Jonah khaw tuili khuila a voeih uh. Te vaengah Pathen loh khohli khaw a paa sak tih Jonah dolh hamla nga a tueih. Nga ko khuiah thangthui tih nga loh tuikaeng la a thaa. Te phoeah Nineveh la cet tih Pathen ol te a pang puei. Khopuei khaw yut tih Pathen loh tholh a hlah pah. A hnukkhueng ah Pathen kah sitlohnah kawng te Jonah a cangpuei.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 I. Tonghma la khuenah neh althanah \ior 1. 1—2. 10\ior*
